225
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:08,080
SEBENARNYA, TETSUTETSU TIADA NIAT JAHAT.

226
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:11,250
TINDAKAN DIA AKAN MEMBANTU KITA.

227
00:12:11,250 --> 00:12:13,370
Honenuki, reaksi awak juga
sangat fleksibel.

228
00:12:14,830 --> 00:12:17,000
Marilah.

