00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:34,500
Bagus.

236
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:36,700
Kita akan serang mereka, kelas A.

237
00:12:36,700 --> 00:12:38,410
Kumpulan ketiga.

238
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,000
TENYA IDA. SIFAT, ENJIN

