303
00:16:06,910 --> 00:16:10,870
Tapi ais dia tak menghalang skrin,
ia dah bertambah baik.

304
00:16:10,870 --> 00:16:13,790
Todoroki berada di arah ais,
mana orang lain?

305
00:16:13,790 --> 00:16:14,870
Saya tak nampak mereka.

306
00:16:15,950 --> 00:16:19,370
Honenuki boleh
melembutkan permukaan tanah,

307
00:16:19,370 --> 00:16:22,790
tapi ia sia-sia saja
selepas ais menutupinya.

308
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:26,700
Kami tangkap mereka sekali gus selepas
pergerakan mereka menjadi perlahan.

309
00:16:30,870 --> 00:16:33,160
Letusan timbal balik.

310
00:16:33,160 --> 00:16:34,910
Marilah.

311
00:16:35,700 --> 00:16:36,580
Apa?

312
00:16:40,660 --> 00:16:43,410
Serangan ais berskala besar terlalu licik.

313
00:16:43,410 --> 00:16:48,080
