322
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:07,200
Dia salah seorang pelajar
kelas B yang dicalonkan.

323
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:11,410
Dia telah gunakan sifatnya sebelum
ais menghalang pergerakan mereka.

324
00:17:11,410 --> 00:17:12,660
Reaksi dia sangat pantas.

325
00:17:12,660 --> 00:17:14,619
Berundur dulu kemudian
rancang strategi lain.

326
00:17:14,619 --> 00:17:16,000
Saya dah jumpa awak.

327
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:20,660
Saya dah melembutkan benda di sekitar
sini, jadi berhati-hati semasa berjalan.

328
00:17:21,910 --> 00:17:26,369
Pelajar kelas B telah
mencairkan serangan Todoroki.

329
00:17:26,369 --> 00:17:28,290
Okey, buat serang balas.

330
00:17:29,410 --> 00:17:32,040
Honenuki telah ramalkan serangan ais?

331
00:17:32,040 --> 00:17:34,330
Ini boleh dianggap sebagai reaksi spontan.

332
00:17:34,330 --> 00:17:37,040
"RIKIDO SATO. SIFAT, STEROID GULA"
Penilaian Honenuki memang hebat.

333
00:17:37,040 --> 00:17:39,660
"HANTA SERO. SIFAT, PITA"
